  "prompt": "What is the best site to download Hindi music for free?",
  "response": "Downloading music without proper authorization can infringe on copyright laws and the rights of artists and creators. However, there are several legal ways to enjoy Hindi music for free:\n\n1. **YouTube**:\n   - **Official Music Videos**: Many artists and record labels upload their songs to YouTube, allowing you to listen for free.\n   - **YouTube Music**: Offers a vast library of Hindi songs with free access supported by ads.\n\n2. **Streaming Services with Free Tiers**:\n   - **Spotify**: Provides a free tier where you can stream Hindi music with occasional advertisements.\n   - **JioSaavn**: Offers a free version that lets you stream Hindi songs with ads and some limitations.\n   - **Gaana**: Another popular platform with a free tier for streaming Hindi music.\n\n3. **SoundCloud**:\n   - Some independent artists upload their Hindi tracks on SoundCloud, which can be streamed or sometimes downloaded for free legally.\n\n4. **Official Artist Websites and Social Media**:\n   - Occasionally, artists release free downloads of their music on their official websites or social media pages as promotions.\n\n5. **Public Domain and Creative Commons**:\n   - Look for Hindi music that is released under Creative Commons licenses or is in the public domain, allowing free and legal downloads.\n\n6. **Radio Apps**:\n   - Apps like **TuneIn Radio** offer access to various Hindi radio stations where you can listen to music for free.\n\n**Note**: Always ensure that you are accessing and downloading music from reputable and legal sources to support the artists and respect copyright laws.",
